definition.value: A continuous coverage policy to ensure availability of a neurosurgeon.

A continuous coverage policy that specifies procedures to ensure that anesthesiology services are available at a healthcare provider organization 24 hours, 7 days a week.

A role that inheres in an organization and, if realized, is realized by the bearer organizing the provision of operative manual and instrumental techniques on a patient's hand to investigate and/or treat a pathological condition such as disease or injury, to help improve bodily function or appearance.

This is not a representation of a professional organization of microvascular sugery providers, but an organization that provides microvascular surgery.

A role that inheres in an organization and, if realized, is realized by the bearer organizing the provision of operative manual and instrumental techniques on a patient's spine to investigate or treat a pathological condition such as disease or injury, to help improve bodily function or appearance.

definition.value: A role that inheres in a human being and, if realized, is realized by representing an emergency department in the quality improvement program of organization providing pre-hospital care and services.

based on the comments from our expert team, this class is modeled to include air medical provides (not to include pilots) and not to include dispatchers.

A collection of humans that only has as members bearers of an anesthesiologist role.
